  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook for 2-3 minutes per side until charred and pink.",
    "Add the kapi paste and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the confit tomato and cook for 2 minutes until heated through.",
    "Stir in the parsley, salt, black pepper, and lemon juice.",
    "Serve the shrimp and sauce hot over your choice of paleo-friendly sides.",
    " Garnish with additional parsley if desired."
